# EPEL Repository Notes

This file is a short reference for enabling and verifying the Extra Packages for Enterprise Linux repository.

## Install The EPEL Release Package

```bash
dnf install https://dl.fedoraproject.org/pub/epel/epel-release-latest-8.noarch.rpm -y
```

## Verify The Repository

```bash
dnf repolist epel
dnf repolist epel -v
```

## List Packages From EPEL

```bash
dnf repository-packages epel list | grep ansible
```

## Notes

- This example targets EPEL on Enterprise Linux style systems.
- Review the EPEL version you need for your operating system before using the command unchanged.
